OL,7,FSarah Adams from was only two years
OL,8,Fold in 1982 when her Haemophiliac
OL,9,Ffather was given blood products
OL,10,Ffollowing a football injury.
OL,12,FThree years later, Alan Burgess
OL,13,Freceived a letter to say that he had
OL,14,Fbeen infected with HIV.
OL,16,FAlan revealed his diagnosis to his
OL,17,Fdaughter when she was 11. She recalls:
OL,18,F"It was the scariest thing I've ever
OL,19,Fbeen told.
