OL,7,F"I was sworn to secrecy wasn't allowed
OL,8,Fto tell a soul, no friends, nobody
OL,9,Fcould know about my dads HIV. Only
OL,10,Fbecause of the stigma.
OL,12,FHe also had his own business at that
OL,13,Ftime, he was a really successful
OL,14,Fpainter and decorator employing
OL,15,Fdifferent people as the work was
OL,16,Fcoming in. And obviously this had to
OL,17,Fbe kept hush hush because he would
OL,18,Flose the work".
