OL,7,FAlan was also infected with Hepatitis
OL,8,FC. For Sarah and her siblings the news
OL,9,Fwas devastating.
OL,11,FShe describes how she and her sister
OL,12,Ffaced the effects of the stigma and
OL,13,Fabuse at school.
OL,15,F"It was a horrible time to be at
OL,16,Fschool," she said.
