OL,7,F"I would get bullied quite a lot at
OL,8,Fschool when people did find out. I was
OL,9,Fon free school meals at the time
OL,10,Fbecause of my dad not working and my
OL,11,Fmum caring for him.
OL,13,F"Because of the bullying at school it
OL,14,Fwas a lot easier for my sister and I
OL,15,Fto not have the meals at all so we
OL,16,Fwouldn't eat at all during the school
OL,17,Fday.
OL,19,F"It was at the time with the adverts.
OL,20,FThe government were putting them out
OL,21,Fthere to try and protect people.
