OL,7,F"In actual fact they did more harm to
OL,8,Fout community than anything. Because
OL,9,Fit just emphasised the danger of
OL,10,Fknowing someone with this horrible
OL,11,Fdisease at the time. It was harrowing".
OL,13,FSarah says that her father suffered
OL,14,Ffrom mental health issues as a result
OL,15,Fof his diagnoses.
OL,17,F"He sadly has had a few mental issues
OL,18,Fand had to have been admitted to the
OL,19,Flocal hospital," she told ITV News
OL,20,FCentral.
