OL,7,F"To place your dad into a mental
OL,8,Fhospital like that and just leave him
OL,9,Fthere like a vulnerable child is a
OL,10,Freally difficult thing to do and I'll
OL,11,Fnever forget the day I had to do that
OL,12,Falong with my Mum.
OL,14,F"He's exhausted, he feels angry, he
OL,15,Ffeels let down, but angry more than
OL,16,Fanything that this was allowed to
OL,17,Fhappen."
