OL,7,FThe findings of the Infected Blood
OL,8,FInquiry will be published on Monday.
OL,9,FSarah wants justice for what has
OL,10,Fhappened to her father and her family.
OL,12,F"I want the truth to come out I want
OL,13,Fpeople to be held accountable for what
OL,14,Fthey did. I want justice at the end of
OL,15,Fthe day," she said.
